Simple solution.  Code it so that it has a short enough range (100), a long enough cast time (3.5), and allow it only to work in groups of 3 to 6.  Obviously the code is there for that... it's pretty much just making sure there are 2 people other than yourself in the group and that you're not in a raid. <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START ;) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/images/emoticons/wink.gif ALT=";)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->   Burn teams are a non issue because if you could do it with those nukes you could do it with Strike of Solusek and probably Draught of Ro (there are already some burn teams out there that use 2 Wizards chaining SoS). <br>
<br>
Example...<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>Exertion of Ro</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--><br>
1400 damage<br>
200 mana<br>
+10 resist modifier<br>
100 ft range<br>
3.5 sec cast time<br>
Instant recast.<br>
<br>
Only works in groups of 3 to 6 and not on raids.<br>
